  "body": "### Description\r\nCurrently, `Eth2GossipTopicFilter` assumes we'll have at most 2 active forks, and calculates which topics are relevant for the current fork and next fork.  We need to update this logic to handle additional fork transitions.  \r\n\r\nSee: https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/03cad2146de627653ebef2091354874d7d488029/networking/eth2/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/networking/eth2/gossip/topics/Eth2GossipTopicFilter.java#L46-L47\r\n",
